            <div class="alert alert-success" id="recent-changes">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">📝 Recent Changes (v1.00 - Jan 9, 2026)</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 5px 0 0 20px;">
                    <li><strong>Initial Documentation:</strong> Created comprehensive documentation for DocumentationRoleAccess model</li>
                    <li><strong>Pattern Matching:</strong> Documented wildcard pattern system for documentation path matching</li>
                    <li><strong>Access Rules:</strong> Documented grant/deny model with role+pattern uniqueness</li>
                </ul>
